<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-300] document filesystem limits in only one place</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-300</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The manual documents the Lustre filesystem limits in both &quot;Table 1.1. Lustre File System Scalability and Performance&quot; and &quot;Table 5.2. File and file system limits&quot;.  This results in inconsistencies and potential confusion, and should be consolidated to a single location with a cross-reference.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
